title: Sid Meiers Civilization Beyond Earth Exoplanets DLC
description:
Sid Meiers Civilization Beyond Earth Exoplanets DLC

This is just the DLC

Extract 7zip to your game folder & play!


The Exoplanets Map Pack includes six custom maps inspired by real exoplanets. These custom maps will offer excellent replayability, as specialized scripts randomly generate different geographic layouts with every game. The six different

Exoplanets included are:

Kepler 186f: This lush forest planet is one of the oldest known Earth-like planets.

Rigil Khantoris Bb: Orbiting the closest star to the solar system, the historical records of this arid continental planetÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s settlement are well-preserved.

Tau Ceti d: This planet of seas and archipelagos features a booming biodiversity and a wealth of resources.

Mu Arae f: Tidally locked in orbit around a weak star, the southern hemisphere of this planet is a blistering desert where the sun never sets, while the northern hemisphere is perpetually in frozen darkness.

82 Eridani e: An alien world of scarce water and wracked by tectonic forces.

Eta Vulpeculae b: A mysterious new discovery with unknown terrain
